					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&#8230;Okay, but I really can't hate the way you use the SPC in this canon. I mean, &quot;We're going to get the Shark Punchers to capture a shark god and turn it loose at its avian nemesis, who caused all this trouble&quot;? That plan's so stupid and outlandish, there's no way it can fail. :D</p> 
				 	]]>
